name: UGameFeatureAction_AddChunkOverride
doc:
Used to cook assets from a GFP into a specified chunkId.
This can be useful when individually cooking GFPs for iteration or splitting up a packaged
game into smaller downloadable chunks.

bShouldOverrideChunk: Should this GFP have their packages cooked into the specified ChunkId
ChunkId: What ChunkId to place the packages inside for this particular GFP.
